<plot>American Gregor Stevens (Scott Brady) arrives in London searching for his brother who, unknown to him, has been convicted of a murder and is within three days of being executed. He meets Yvonne Durante (Mary Castle), a night-club entertainer and part-time smuggler, who aids him in his quest to prove the innocence of his brother, despite the risks she faces from her diamond-smuggling confederates.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?605919</url></doc>
